1、No man will make a great leader who wants to do it all himself or get all the credit for doing it.

没有人能成为伟大的领导者，如果他什么事都想自己来或者想从中获得所有的声望。

2、The way to become rich is to put all your eggs in one basket and then watch that basket.

变得富有的方式就是把所有的鸡蛋都放在一个篮子里然后看着它。

3、You cannot push any one up a ladder unless he be willing to climb a little himself.

你无法把一个人推上一个梯子，除非他自己想要爬上那么一点点。

------Andraw Carnegie(1835-1919)


1、Applause is a receipt,not a bill.

掌声是发自内心的，而非有偿。

2、If you want to conquer fear,don't sit home and think about it.Go out and get busy.

如果你想克服恐惧，不要干坐在家里只是想想。走出去忙起来。

3、People rarely succeed unless  they have fun in what they are doing.

人往往很难成功，除非他们对自己所做的事情感兴趣。

------Dale Carnegie(1888-1955)


